{"tid":772410,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] Art of War 3 即時軍事戰略遊戲RTS","createTime":"2018-08-08T17:19:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T16:22:45.000Z","uid":9829,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e9c9f39e033296e8f62fbedcd01b7a0aee032e3a","tid":772410,"uid":9829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T17:19:01.000Z","msg":"呢個game喺香港冇人玩我覺得好可惜<br />\n希望呢度可以帶動到多啲人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人認為呢個係mobile入面最好玩最正宗嘅Real Time Strategy game<br />\n入面有得打真人1v1/2v2 or打電腦<br />\n喺一個大地圖入面你要起基地同打人<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/09/011728_3470df6186ff4c2567da6e24a784c556.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2F011728_3470df6186ff4c2567da6e24a784c556.png&h=1cc59be0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左上角map<br />\n一開始成個圖都黑哂要派兵睇<br />\n會有野生能源比你執<br />\n能源係資源，你起兵/起野都會消費佢<br />\n 電係容量，每個建築都會有個cost<br />\n過咗會起唔到野<br />\nCP係兵力上限，升總部可以升佢<br />\n<br />\nGame Features<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你可以控制每一隻兵行去邊，打邊個，去邊度巡邏etc<br />\n亦有唔同戰略同打仗一樣<br />\n例如引走人地啲兵/埋伏<br />\n做錯決定好易比人反勝<br />\n有繁體中文有香港旗<br />\n畫質好高質好靚<br />\n分咗2個陣營<br />\nBlue-裝備比較好<br />\nRed-可以隱藏<br />\n每個陣營啲兵種都唔同<br />\n而且重課幫助唔大比較公平<br />\n（主要秒科技進度）<br />\n兵種亦分咗海陸空三軍每種都會剋人同比人剋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGame 名: Art of War 3<br />\n快啲down嚟試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016e55e096b11f4d2872e9534815faa91038e751","tid":772410,"uid":9829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T17:20:05.000Z","msg":"打住咁多先聽日再介紹啲兵種<br />\n有問題可以即管問希望可以幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd25236e9fdfbc97b0607d42a4238992a08d295c","tid":772410,"uid":9829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T17:20:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1235106bf1369829d7dded8af0e052651b3b8aa5","tid":772410,"uid":9829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T01:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3156f09a8f39745fb848b86c9fb3160dd8ca5c","tid":772410,"uid":9829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T02:54:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4cca0c4e5cb9b0e090f82d2e835b483e58dfc47","tid":772410,"uid":9829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T15:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f7518d964937f96ff61e0abfbdc2f42a679beb","tid":772410,"uid":9829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T18:08:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda2a01b94dd5a56ecba2039abd940303c42d4c6","tid":772410,"uid":12633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T02:04:05.000Z","msg":"你介紹多小小"},{"pid":"f41e0ced3626af17db2f2cc56ce7fe461adea90a","tid":772410,"uid":9829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:08:24.000Z","msg":"好感動有人應<br />\n呢度有條宣傳片<br />\n入面嘅野全部都可以喺game入面做<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4AfmuU7vW08\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4AfmuU7vW08&d=f%2B%2FQirMgScEj7oV8hhiYmxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=046612de\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4AfmuU7vW08</a><br />\n<br />\n下面介紹下啲兵種<br />\n分咗海陸空三軍同三個lv嘅兵<br />\n另外重有特殊兵種<br />\n<br />\n先係我用緊嘅藍色<br />\n陸軍士兵（對空冇用）<br />\nLv1係揸步槍，主要拎嚟一開始偵查地圖同搶資源<br />\n比機關槍/火counter<br />\nLv2拎火箭筒，主要打車類同坦克<br />\n但打士兵冇用<br />\nLv3揸噴火器專殺士兵<br />\n<br />\n陸軍坦克（最主要兵）<br />\nLv1衝鋒車<br />\n有機關槍同火，可以偵測地雷<br />\n主剋士兵，唔夠大炮打<br />\n可對空<br />\n<br />\nLv2微型坦克<br />\n小型炮剋車類<br />\n但打土兵冇咩用<br />\n不能對空<br />\n<br />\nLv3坦克<br />\n巨炮範圍傷可以指定地方轟<br />\n另有導彈可以對空<br />\n打土兵冇打坦克咁痛<br />\n通常後期鬥邊個多<br />\n<br />\n特殊兵<br />\nLv1對空飛彈車<br />\n只能對空<br />\n可變型態冇得郁但遠啲痛啲<br />\n<br />\nLv2導彈車<br />\n只對地要變型態可以揀地方炸但冇得郁<br />\n傷害痛射程遠<br />\n<br />\nLv3盾車<br />\n冇輸出開個範圍盾周圍行<br />\n<br />\n空軍<br />\nLv1直升機<br />\n可無限飛用機槍主打士兵<br />\n<br />\nLv2戰機<br />\n要起降落台先用得<br />\n飛一次內會打目標幾次<br />\n之後返嚟補油<br />\n<br />\nLv3轟炸機<br />\n炸一次補一次<br />\n好撚痛<br />\n<br />\n海軍<br />\nLv1小船<br />\n機關槍同小炮<br />\n單挑嬴紅軍lv1<br />\n可查地雷<br />\n<br />\nLv2驅逐艦<br />\n得大炮同魚雷<br />\n打lv1無敵<br />\n<br />\nLv3轟炸艦<br />\n揀地方炸遠同痛<br />\n有對空彈<br />\n忌比船埋身"},{"pid":"bd6a968a7cbf561c244997b48da22c3646a2beb3","tid":772410,"uid":9829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:10:29.000Z","msg":"紅軍<br />\n未用過所以可能有漏/唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n士兵lv1/2一樣<br />\nLv3未見過<br />\n<br />\n車lv1可以放地雷<br />\n用機關槍<br />\n<br />\nLv2有槍有小炮<br />\n可放地雷<br />\n<br />\nLv3坦克可變型態<br />\n<br />\n特殊車lv1 機關槍＋對空彈<br />\nLv2 同藍軍一樣<br />\nLv3係冇攻擊<br />\n但放迷霧對面睇唔到入面有咩<br />\n<br />\n空軍lv1機關槍+導彈<br />\nLv2 戰機same<br />\nLv3 轟炸機same但範圍大啲<br />\n<br />\n海軍lv1 機關槍同放地雷<br />\nLv2 大炮同對空飛彈<br />\nLv3 係潛艇空軍飛過見唔到<br />\n得海軍見到同魚雷打到<br />\n攻擊凈係知有魚雷<br />\n好似可以用轟炸<br />\n<br />\n同埋有個藍軍top player嘅YouTube channel<br />\n可以睇下人地點打同啲策略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCjOEupXeNLNbQk8LtVrSxJQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCjOEupXeNLNbQk8LtVrSxJQ&d=f%2B%2FQirMgScEj7oV8hhiYmxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=53258132\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCjOEupXeNLNbQk8LtVrSxJQ</a><br />\n下次講下加成<br />\n希望有人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ba6151b0ca826bc07a84c0c427b505e99936ca","tid":772410,"uid":9829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T16:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"147c35f3d4e071792c19880645525d6a7457c483","tid":772410,"uid":9829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T00:15:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ed428bda6f676aab5559c43bd45a1b3ccdb041","tid":772410,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T03:42:01.000Z","msg":"隻game有冇story mode, 定係好似clash royale呢d一盤打幾分鐘,完事又等下一鋪?"},{"pid":"fc7ac82928ee15db72567aadf58e87d288ddb5fe","tid":772410,"uid":9829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0ed428bda6f676aab5559c43bd45a1b3ccdb041","tid":772410,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T03:42:01.000Z","msg":"隻game有冇story mode, 定係好似clash royale呢d一盤打幾分鐘,完事又等下一鋪?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:41:22.000Z","msg":"隻game有4個mode<br />\n第一個係story mode<br />\n紅軍50關藍軍50關<br />\n個game有第二帳號係你冇揀果個陣營<br />\n類似重頭開始但另一邊<br />\n<br />\n第二個mode係世界戰<br />\n分咗20個區每次開一個<br />\n1v1/2v2 有3個type嘅地圖<br />\n1-霸旗仔拎分拎到一個分<br />\n對面霸返到佢加分你減分<br />\n2-有旗仔霸加資源但要打爆對面<br />\n3-隊冧佢<br />\n<br />\n一場正常5-20分鐘耐啲都有可能<br />\n贏咗=陣營加分睇下邊個拎到個區<br />\n完咗一個區就派錢<br />\n<br />\n錢用嚟升科技非常重要<br />\n或者買加成<br />\n有30幾種每種分3個lv<br />\n得2種lv3冇得用假錢買不過佢地冇乜用<br />\n<br />\n第三個mode係公會戰<br />\n以公會型式唔用陣營但通常藍vs紅<br />\n每次地圖有唔同目標/限制<br />\n最後有排名派獎勵<br />\n暫時見過嘅香港人少過5個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台灣20個內 蝗蟲多少少但主要外國人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第四個mode係2個人一齊打Ai<br />\n好撚難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07eb40ac5ba9cdf5005d38670d75286dd9bf703","tid":772410,"uid":9829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T05:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/13/134146_934e65a47a65f7272ad081f533cf65ff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F13%2F134146_934e65a47a65f7272ad081f533cf65ff.png&h=a9589830&s={SIZE}\" 